Class DefaultXMLFile

java.lang.Object
  ibbt.sumo.gui.context.DefaultXMLFile
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConfigXMLFile
public class DefaultXMLFile
extends java.lang.Object

This class loads an default xml and is used to read config elements necessery for initialization of create plan and add run dialogs. And all the other options are read from this file.

Author:
Sasa Berberovic
